00230 inline void erreur_non_convergence()
00231 {
00232   Cerr << "TRUST stopped cause in the function calculer_u_plus of wall law." << finl;
00233   Cerr << "The iterative process of u* did not converge" << finl;
00234   if (Process::nproc()>1) Cerr << " on the processor" << Process::me();
